
<div class="row">
  <div class="span12">

    <!--// BEGIN BANNER CAROUSEL -->
    <div id="banner-carousel" class="carousel slide">

      <div class="carousel-inner">

        <div class="active item" style="height:325px;">
          <div style="position:absolute; top:80px; left:60px;"><h1 style="font-size:40px">Search.</h1></div>
          <%= image_tag "banner_1.jpg" %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <p>Search and learn about the saints of the Catholic Church using Saintstir's interactive filter buttons.  Every wonder which saints are
            known for particular virtues or superpowers?  Interested in finding saints who went through the same struggles that you are going through?
            Find this with our saint explorer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="item" style="height:325px;">
          <div style="position:absolute; top:80px; left:60px;"><h1 style="font-size:40px">Discover.</h1></div>
          <%= image_tag "banner_2.jpg" %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <p>Find out more about the Catholic saints, beyond facts and biographies.  Read their quotes for inspiration, and discover other
            saints with similar traits and graces.  Read stories, testimonies, and prayers from site members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="item" style="height:325px;">
          <div style="position:absolute; top:80px; left:60px;"><h1 style="font-size:40px">Venerate.</h1></div>
          <%= image_tag "banner_3.jpg" %>
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <p>Honor and venerate the saints of the church with other members and contributors.  Share your reflections with others on Facebook, Google, and Twitter.
            Leave reflections and prayers on the saint's "wall".  "Like" other member's reflections.  Build a community through Saintstir.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Carousel nav -->
      <a class="carousel-control left" href="#banner-carousel" data-slide="prev">&lsaquo;</a>
      <a class="carousel-control right" href="#banner-carousel" data-slide="next">&rsaquo;</a>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

